v class=\"comp comp-3\">\n            <div class=\"comp-body !gap-6\">\n                              <figure>\n                  <video\n                    playsinline\n                    data-autoplay-in-viewport=\"true\"\n                    preload=\"none\"\n                    muted\n                    loop\n                                      <source\n                    type=\"video\/mp4\"\n                    data-src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Creative-Brand-Design-Showreel-V2.mp4\" \/>\n                  Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                  <\/video>\n                <\/figure>\n                                            <figure>\n                  <img width=\"700\" height=\"467\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/CBD-First-Lot-10.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"website design agency office fish\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/CBD-First-Lot-10.webp 700w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/CBD-First-Lot-10-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/CBD-First-Lot-10-576x384.webp 576w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                <\/figure>\n                                            <figure>\n                  <img width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/cbd-team7_wide.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"web design agency client meeting\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/cbd-team7_wide.webp 1000w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/cbd-team7_wide-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/cbd-team7_wide-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/cbd-team7_wide-576x384.webp 576w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                <\/figure>\n                          <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"w-full sm:w-5\/12 mt-12 sm:mb-0\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n                                <h3>Our Values<\/h3>\n                                <div\n              class=\"content sm:w-11\/12 lg:w-full\">\n              <p>We\u2019re all about positivity, celebrating achievements, and recognising everyone\u2019s contributions. Instead of focusing on challenges, we\u2019re creating an uplifting, supportive vibe. Our studio strikes the perfect balance between creative and professional, with flexible hours to keep work-life balance in check. Our team\u2019s global, so you can work from wherever suits you best. If your birthday\u2019s on a weekday, expect a team meal or drinks to celebrate, and for those in the office, snacks and drinks are always on hand to keep you going. We\u2019re here to support your growth and make sure every day\u2019s a win for you and the team.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n                            <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- jobs-accordion --><section class=\"section jobs-accordion\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-center\">\n      <div class=\"w-full md:w-3\/4 xl:w-1\/2\">\n        <!-- Header -->\n        <div class=\"header\">\n                                <div class=\"subtitle\">\n              <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <use href=\"#dot\"><\/use> <\/svg>\n              Open Positions            <\/div>\n                                <h2>Explore Exciting Career Opportunities with Us<\/h2>\n                  <\/div>\n        <!-- Accordion -->\n        <div class=\"accordion\">\n                      <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n              <div class=\"accordion-item-title\" data-cursor=\"collapse\" data-collapsed=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"inner\">\n                                      <h4 class=\"font-primary\">Junior Front-End Developer<\/h4>\n                                    <ul class=\"tags\">\n                                            <li>Semi Remote<\/li>\n                                            <li>Development<\/li>\n                                      <\/ul>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n              <\/div>\n              <div class=\"accordion-item-content bordered\">\n                <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner\">\n                  <div class=\"row gap-6\">\n                    <div class=\"sm:w-8\/12 wysiwyg\">\n                                              <h5 class=\"font-primary mb-2\">Overview<\/h5>\n                        <p class=\"text-sm\"><p><strong>The Role:<\/strong><br \/>As a Junior Front-End Developer, you&rsquo;ll bring designs to life by focusing on user experience, interactivity, and animation. While you don&rsquo;t need to have extensive coding experience, a strong eye for design, creativity, and a willingness to learn are essential. This is a great opportunity to develop your coding skills while contributing to visually engaging and interactive web projects.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What We&rsquo;re Looking For:<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A passion for design and interactivity &ndash; you enjoy creating things that feel alive!<\/li>\r\n<li>A basic understanding of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript &ndash; advanced skills are a bonus but not required.<\/li>\r\n<li>Experience or interest in animation tools (e.g., GSAP, Lottie, or Spline) and creating smooth user interactions.<\/li>\r\n<li>A keen eye for detail and appreciation for good design.<\/li>\r\n<li>A portfolio showcasing your creativity &ndash; this could be personal projects, design work, or interactive experiments.<\/li>\r\n<li>An eagerness to learn and grow in a supportive, creative team environment.<\/li>\r\n<li>A good understanding of Adobe, Figma, or similar design tools is a bonus.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul><\/p>\n                                                                    <h5 class=\"font-primary mb-2 mt-8\">Key Tasks<\/h5>\n                        <p class=\"text-sm\"><p><strong>What You&rsquo;ll Be Doing:<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Collaborating with designers and developers to translate creative concepts into engaging, responsive web experiences.<\/li>\r\n<li>Implementing interactive elements and animations to elevate user experiences using libraries like GSAP or similar tools.<\/li>\r\n<li>Building and maintaining websites with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript (basic knowledge required &ndash; we&rsquo;ll help you grow!).<\/li>\r\n<li>Ensuring designs are implemented with pixel-perfect attention to detail.<\/li>\r\n<li>Testing and troubleshooting across browsers and devices to ensure compatibility and performance.<\/li>\r\n<li>Learning and contributing to the development of new ideas, techniques, and trends in design and front-end development.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul><\/p>\n                                          <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"sm:flex-1\">\n                      <dl class=\"description\">\n                                                  <dt>Location<\/dt>\n                          <dd>Semi Remote, Surrey<\/dd>\n                                                                          <dt>Salary<\/dt>\n                          <dd>Based on Experience <\/dd>\n                                              <\/dl>\n                                              <a\n                          href=\"mailto:info@creativebranddesign.com?subject=Junior%20Front%20End%20Developer\"\n                          target=\"_self\"\n                          class=\"btn btn-outline mt-4\"\n                          data-mp>\n                          <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n                          <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item>Email us<\/span>\n                        <\/a>\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                      <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n              <div class=\"accordion-item-title\" data-cursor=\"collapse\" data-collapsed=\"true\">\n                <div class=\"inner\">\n                                      <h4 class=\"font-primary\">Copywriter (Part\/Full-Time)<\/h4>\n                                    <ul class=\"tags\">\n                                            <li>Remote<\/li>\n                                            <li>Copywriting<\/li>\n                                      <\/ul>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n              <\/div>\n              <div class=\"accordion-item-content bordered\">\n                <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner\">\n                  <div class=\"row gap-6\">\n                    <div class=\"sm:w-8\/12 wysiwyg\">\n                                              <h5 class=\"font-primary mb-2\">Overview<\/h5>\n                        <p class=\"text-sm\"><p><strong>The Role:<\/strong><br \/>We&rsquo;re seeking a creative and detail-oriented Copywriter to produce engaging and effective content for websites, marketing materials, and digital campaigns. Whether you&rsquo;re looking for part-time flexibility or a full-time role, this is an opportunity to work on diverse projects that allow your writing skills to shine.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What We&rsquo;re Looking For:<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Proven experience in copywriting, content creation, or a related field (agency experience is a bonus).<\/li>\r\n<li>Excellent written English with impeccable grammar and attention to detail.<\/li>\r\n<li>A portfolio showcasing a variety of writing styles, from engaging headlines to in-depth articles.<\/li>\r\n<li>A good understanding of SEO principles and how to write for search engines without sacrificing creativity.<\/li>\r\n<li>Ability to adapt writing tone and style to suit different brands and industries.<\/li>\r\n<li>Strong organisational skills and the ability to manage multiple projects and deadlines.<\/li>\r\n<li>Experience with content management systems (e.g., WordPress) is a bonus.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Flexibility: Choose part-time or full-time hours to suit your lifestyle.<\/li>\r\n<li>Work on exciting, high-profile projects across various industries.<\/li>\r\n<li>Join a supportive and collaborative team where your ideas are valued.<\/li>\r\n<li>Opportunities for professional growth and development.<\/li>\r\n<li>Flexible working options &ndash; hybrid or remote.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul><\/p>\n                                                                    <h5 class=\"font-primary mb-2 mt-8\">Key Tasks<\/h5>\n                        <p class=\"text-sm\"><p><strong>What You&rsquo;ll Be Doing:<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Writing clear, engaging, and SEO-optimized website copy, blog articles, and marketing content.<\/li>\r\n<li>Collaborating with designers, developers, and clients to align content with brand tone and objectives.<\/li>\r\n<li>Conducting research to understand target audiences and industries, ensuring content is relevant and impactful.<\/li>\r\n<li>Creating compelling headlines, CTAs, and microcopy to improve user journeys.<\/li>\r\n<li>Proofreading and editing to ensure consistency and a polished final product.<\/li>\r\n<li>Assisting with content strategy, including user personas, messaging frameworks, and tone of voice guidelines.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul><\/p>\n                                          <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"sm:flex-1\">\n                      <dl class=\"description\">\n                                                  <dt>Location<\/dt>\n                          <dd>Remote <\/dd>\n                                                                          <dt>Salary<\/dt>\n                          <dd>Based on Experience<\/dd>\n                                              <\/dl>\n                                              <a\n                          href=\"mailto:info@creativebranddesign.com?subject=Copywriter \"\n                          target=\"_self\"\n                          class=\"btn btn-outline mt-4\"\n                          data-mp>\n                          <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n                          <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item>Email us<\/span>\n                        <\/a>\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                  <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-2881","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2881","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.